 John, welcome to Feel the Boot. Thanks so much for having me. So, we've talked a

00:01:18.440 --> 00:01:22.400
 little bit before this recording. And we exchanged some emails. Why don't you tell

00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:27.000
 us a little bit just for context of what your startup does?

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:32.080
 Yeah. So, my startup is named is called Pick Food. You can think of Pick Food as

