 a digital focus group. So, the same way that large brands and CPGs, like Procter

00:01:38.240 --> 00:01:45.200
 and Gamble, use large focus groups to figure out their product packaging, testing, marketing,

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:51.400
 all of that stuff. Pick Food lets you do that in a self service way. And we tap into

00:01:51.400 --> 00:01:57.680
 the same global consumer panels that are used by the large CPGs. So, Pick Food as

00:01:57.680 --> 00:02:02.840
 self service. You can come on the site, choose your target audience, ask a question, post

